774
00:58:30,924 --> 00:58:32,467
Anyway, just think about it.

775
00:58:34,135 --> 00:58:36,387
It'd be nice for broken people

776
00:58:37,096 --> 00:58:38,681
to support each other.

777
00:58:59,369 --> 00:59:00,662
Your father

778
00:59:00,745 --> 00:59:02,664
waited for two whole hours.

779
00:59:03,498 --> 00:59:06,042
Is it that hard for you
to see your father?

780
00:59:07,794 --> 00:59:08,753
I'm sorry.

781
00:59:09,420 --> 00:59:10,838
Let's set another date.

782
00:59:11,965 --> 00:59:13,216
I'll be in touch.

783
00:59:13,925 --> 00:59:15,093
Wait, Moo-young.

784
00:59:15,927 --> 00:59:17,136
I'm sorry.

785
00:59:41,619 --> 00:59:44,455
DIRECTOR OF NAVIS WELL-BEING
JANG KYUNG-JA

786
01:00:17,697 --> 01:00:18,865
What are you doing?

787
01:00:22,994 --> 01:00:25,371
It'd be nice for broken people

788
01:00:26,164 --> 01:00:27,832
