789
01:00:56,653 --> 01:00:58,196
Oh, I remember.

790
01:01:00,073 --> 01:01:01,407
What was your name again?

791
01:01:04,494 --> 01:01:05,453
It's Su-ho.

792
01:01:06,371 --> 01:01:07,246
Na Su-ho.

793
01:01:08,122 --> 01:01:09,415
Right, Su-ho.

794
01:01:10,625 --> 01:01:13,294
If you take me in,
I'll work really hard for you.

795
01:01:14,337 --> 01:01:15,296
Good.

796
01:01:16,464 --> 01:01:17,298
But first,

797
01:01:18,007 --> 01:01:19,884
I need you tell me.

798
01:01:21,678 --> 01:01:24,806
What was Lee Ro-eum
trying to steal from Kyung-ja?

799
01:01:37,485 --> 01:01:38,361
Ro-eum.

800
01:01:39,654 --> 01:01:40,488
Hey.

801
01:01:44,701 --> 01:01:46,119
What's going on?

