Who?

804
01:01:48,788 --> 01:01:50,748
Someone who'll be helping us.

805
01:01:52,250 --> 01:01:53,668
Say hello.

806
01:01:55,461 --> 01:01:56,295
This is Jay.

807
01:02:04,303 --> 01:02:05,179
We meet again.

808
01:02:40,882 --> 01:02:42,049
From now on,

809
01:02:42,133 --> 01:02:43,760
you won't be the one talking to that man.

810
01:02:43,843 --> 01:02:45,094
Why don't you like me?

811
01:02:45,178 --> 01:02:46,471
Do I have to like you?

812
01:02:46,554 --> 01:02:49,348
I don't want you to see her.
There's no knowing what I'll do to her.

813
01:02:49,432 --> 01:02:50,808
I wish you'd bring him in.

814
01:02:50,892 --> 01:02:52,643
Not Jay. Na-sa.

815
01:02:52,727 --> 01:02:55,563
You're not that kid anymore.
If they beat you, bite them back at least.

816
01:02:55,646 --> 01:02:58,566
Don't you realize that people are willing
to be in this together with you?

817
01:02:58,649 --> 01:03:00,151
It's fantasy, not empathy.

818
01:03:00,234 --> 01:03:01,986
And it's delusion, not feelings.

819
01:03:02,069 --> 01:03:03,404
No wonder it's an illness.

820
01:03:03,488 --> 01:03:06,449
But the person who will
help you until the very end is me,

821
01:03:06,532 --> 01:03:07,492
not Jay.

